通过不断地增加支付系统（例如欧洲的Skrill<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://moneynews.ru/News/15417/ |title=Xsolla начала сотрудничать со Skrill |access-date=2013-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113035615/http://moneynews.ru/News/15417/ |archive-date=2018-01-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>以及SafetyPay<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.paymentobserver.com/xsolla-safetypay-monetize-online-games-3769 |title=Xsolla and SafetyPay Join Forces To Monetize Online Games |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202224948/http://www.paymentobserver.com/xsolla-safetypay-monetize-online-games-3769 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，这是在48个国家<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.centili.com/blog/2013/04/centili-via-xsolla-now-available-in-48-countries/ |title=Centili Official Website |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2013-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920021530/https://www.centili.com/blog/2013/04/centili-via-xsolla-now-available-in-48-countries/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>中使用的支付系统）和游戏开发者/发行者（Barbily<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mondespersistants.com/news/star-supremacy-star-supremacy-choisi-xsolla:20490/ |title=Star Supremacy choisi Xsolla |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202232336/http://www.mondespersistants.com/news/star-supremacy-star-supremacy-choisi-xsolla%3A20490/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、 S2 Games<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://geek.digitalspad.com/S2-Games-chooses-to-Xsolla-payment-solution-in-the-world-of-game/ |title=S2 Games Chooses To Xsolla Payment Solution In The World Of Game |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2013-09-05 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130905001838/http://geek.digitalspad.com/S2-Games-chooses-to-Xsolla-payment-solution-in-the-world-of-game/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、Valve<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamer.ru/everything/xsolla-i-valve-anonsirovali-platezhnuyu-sistemu-dlya-steam-v-rossii |title=Xsolla и Valve анонсировали платежную систему для Steam в России |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2018-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113093240/http://www.gamer.ru/everything/xsolla-i-valve-anonsirovali-platezhnuyu-sistemu-dlya-steam-v-rossii |dead-url=no }}</ref>，等等），公司的业务迅速地扩张到全球多个地区。

